Grimacing in pain the stunned ball boy spun around after being hit and briefly tried to walk it off.

But he soon got down on one knee to get his breath back as a worried Lopez then walked down the court to make sure he was all right.

The umpire and players stood around the teenager giving words of encouragement, but they could do little to ease his pain.  

